extendedInfo.description: Search for books, DVDs, audiobooks, CDs, and more! The search feature in the catalog is easy to use and will allow you to find the materials you are looking for in no time! Looking to download books to your wireless device? You can link to our eMedia Library! You can even login into your account and place holds and renew items.Not only can you access the catalog from your phone, you can also view the calendar and see what events are scheduled at the library. Check out library hours and connect with us through social media too!
